HEADWORD: Reimport
<hw>Re`im*port"</hw> <pr>(-p?rt")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>import</ets>: cf. F. <ets>remporter</ets>.]</ety>
